description: Enigma-Bulwark, Limited, an integrated security and risk management company, delivers security solutions for governments, corporations, and individuals worldwide. It provides protective security solutions for high-volume resort hotels and events, multi-national corporations, high net worth individuals, NGOs, and private organizations; maritime security innovative solutions for the purpose of tracking commercial assets utilizing wire-free autonomous technology; and custom security solutions for premium resort hotels and resorts, visible heavy trafficked events, and personal security. The company was formerly known as Peartrack Security Systems, Inc. Enigma-Bulwark, Limited is headquartered in Los Angeles, California.
